Order Of Precendence
Ist : ASIBLE_CONFIG varaible 
2nd:  ansible.cfg in current directory 
3rd: .ansible.cfg in current user home directory
last: etc/ansible/ansible.cfg

To remove password: sudo visudo --> NOPASSWD: ALL

